# Navigation Consistency Standards

All navigation components must use consistent patterns for active states, typography, icons, and interactions.

## 1. Active State Color

**Use International Orange for all navigation active states:**

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - Consistent active state
<Link
  href="/tasks"
  className={cn(
    "transition-colors",
    isActive
      ? "text-international-orange font-semibold"
      : "text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground"
  )}
>
  Tasks
</Link>

// ❌ WRONG - Don't use other colors for active state
<Link className={isActive ? "text-cyan-600" : ""}>  // Wrong
<Link className={isActive ? "bg-cyan-50" : ""}>  // Wrong
```

**Exception:** Tabs component uses `data-[state=active]:bg-background` which is acceptable for its design.

## 2. Navigation Typography

**Use consistent font sizes and weights:**

```tsx
// Desktop sidebar navigation
<Link
  className={cn(
    "text-sm font-medium",  // Consistent size
    isActive && "font-semibold"
  )}
>
  Dashboard
</Link>

// Mobile bottom navigation
<Link
  className={cn(
    "text-xs font-medium",  // Smaller for mobile
    isActive && "font-semibold"
  )}
>
  Tasks
</Link>

// Marketing navigation
<Link className="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
  Features
</Link>

// ❌ WRONG - Don't use inconsistent sizes
<Link className="text-base">  // Too large
<Link className="text-[10px]">  // Custom size
```

**Standards:**
- Desktop sidebar: `text-sm font-medium`
- Mobile bottom nav: `text-xs font-medium`
- Marketing nav: `text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase`
- Dropdown items: `text-sm font-medium`

## 3. Icon Sizing

**Use consistent icon sizes across navigation:**

```tsx
// Desktop sidebar icons
<Home className="h-4 w-4 mr-3" />

// Mobile navigation icons
<Home className="h-5 w-5" />

// Dropdown menu icons
<Settings className="h-4 w-4" />

// ❌ WRONG - Don't use inconsistent icon sizes
<Home className="h-6 w-6" />  // Too large for desktop nav
<Home className="h-3 w-3" />  // Too small
```

**Standards:**
- Desktop sidebar: `h-4 w-4` with `mr-3` margin
- Mobile bottom nav main items: `h-5 w-5`
- Dropdown menus: `h-4 w-4` with `gap-2`
- Icon-only buttons: `h-4 w-4`

## 4. Icon Color

**Use consistent icon colors:**

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - Icon color matches text
<Link
  className={cn(
    isActive ? "text-international-orange" : "text-muted-foreground"
  )}
>
  <Home className="h-4 w-4" />  {/* Inherits color from parent */}
