```

## Quick Checklist

Before committing any navigation:

- [ ] Active state uses `text-international-orange` (not cyan)
- [ ] Typography consistent: `text-sm font-medium` (desktop), `text-xs` (mobile)
- [ ] Icons consistent: `h-4 w-4` (desktop sidebar), `h-5 w-5` (mobile)
- [ ] Icon color inherits from parent (no manual coloring)
- [ ] Hover states use `transition-colors`
- [ ] Desktop nav uses `gap-3` and `mr-3` for icon spacing
- [ ] Mobile nav items have `min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]`
- [ ] Dropdown items have `min-h-[44px]` and `gap-2`
- [ ] Active items have `font-semibold`
- [ ] Breadcrumbs use `ChevronRight` separator
- [ ] Tabs use Tabs component (not custom)
- [ ] Marketing nav uses uppercase tracking
